### JetBrains IDE (PyCharm/IntelliJ) ###
.idea/workspace.xml
.idea/usage.statistics.xml
.idea/dictionaries
.idea/shelf
# Optional: Sometimes safe to ignore in PyCharm if it causes conflicts
.idea/modules.xml

### Python Specific (CRITICAL) ###
# Python compiles files into these "cache" folders. Never commit them.
__pycache__/
*.pyc

### Virtual Environments ###
# If you create a virtual environment, it puts thousands of files here.
# Never commit your environment libraries.
venv/
.venv/
env/

### Operating System Junk ###
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db